{"meta":{"title":"HycBlog","subtitle":"","description":"","author":"Hyc","url":"https://Hyc-CodeRoad.github.io.git","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"404 Not Found：该页无法显示","date":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.338Z","updated":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.338Z","comments":false,"path":"/404.html","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/404.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"","date":"2022-06-26T04:38:13.271Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:18.000Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":"个人信息 📱手机：18072392773 📞微信：Hyc123_WeChat 📧邮箱：&#x68;&#x79;&#x63;&#x31;&#x32;&#51;&#x5f;&#101;&#109;&#x61;&#x69;&#108;&#x40;&#49;&#54;&#51;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#109; 💻博客：HycBlog (hyc-coderoad.github.io) 专业技能 熟练使用Java面向对象编程，了解JVM以及调优 熟练使用Spring，SpringMVC，MyBatis，MyBatis-Plus，SpringBoot等框架 熟悉MySQL，熟练编写SQL语句，了解MySQL性能调优，了解Oracle，Redis数据库 熟练使用HTML和CSS，JavaScript等前端基础，熟练使用Vue以及ElementUI，Vant，Echarts等前端库 熟练使用Git，Maven，IDEA，VsCode等开发工具 了解Go，Python等语言基础，可以使用Go语言框架GoFrame开发后端接口 了解Docker，Nginx等其他技术，了解Linux基本命令 工作经历浙江财渔科技有限公司 Java开发工程师 2021-03-15 ~ 2022-01-28 北京北龙青云科技有限公司 Java开发工程师 2022-02-28 ~ 至今 项目经验智慧校园（SpringBoot+MyBatis+MySQL+Vue+钉钉小程序） 浙江财渔科技有限公司 使用Vue+VantUI开发前端页面，使用Echarts开发统计相关功能 负责家长大学，智慧校车，放心吃等模块的设计和接口开发 企业ERP系统（GoFrame+MySQL+Angular）浙江财渔科技有限公司 * 中科院人才库/中科院域名管理系统/其他小工具（SpringBoot+MyBatis-Plus+Vue+Oracle） 北京北龙青云科技有限公司 个人总结对自己的定位：后端开发。以全栈为目标，希望成为一个六边形战士。"},{"title":"书单","date":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.340Z","updated":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.340Z","comments":false,"path":"books/index.html","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/books/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"友情链接","date":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.341Z","updated":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.341Z","comments":true,"path":"links/index.html","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/links/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"分类","date":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.341Z","updated":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.341Z","comments":false,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"Repositories","date":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.342Z","updated":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.342Z","comments":false,"path":"repository/index.html","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/repository/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"标签","date":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.342Z","updated":"2022-06-18T13:48:38.342Z","comments":false,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"JWT","slug":"其他/JWT","date":"2022-06-26T04:37:55.786Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"其他/JWT/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/JWT/","excerpt":"","text":"JWT概述SpringBoot整合JWT","categories":[{"name":"其他","slug":"其他","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/categories/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/"}],"tags":[]},{"title":"前端Base64转file类型","slug":"常用代码&开发中的问题/前端Base64转file类型","date":"2022-06-26T04:37:55.758Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:18.000Z","comments":true,"path":"常用代码&开发中的问题/前端Base64转file类型/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81&%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AFBase64%E8%BD%ACfile%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/","excerpt":"","text":"功能背景现有一个域名管理系统，需要上传申请原件（图片）到数据库，现在是将图片以二进制形式直接存储到数据库中。在执行修改操作时，后端返回给前端的为base64格式的照片，如果没有修改原件，重新上传后端使用MultipartFile就无法接收成功。所以需要将base64格式的照片重新转成file格式。 base64直接转file这种方式可能存在兼容性问题。 123456789101112131415//将base64转换为文件 dataURLtoFile: function(data, filename) &#123; var arr = data.split(&#x27;,&#x27;), mime = arr[0].match(/:(.*?);/)[1], bstr = atob(arr[1]), n = bstr.length, u8arr = new Uint8Array(n); while (n--) &#123; u8arr[n] = bstr.charCodeAt(n); &#125; return new File([u8arr], filename, &#123; type: mime &#125;); &#125;, //调用 var file = dataURLtoFile(base64Data, imgName); base64转成bolb，blob再转成file格式这种方式可以解决兼容性问题。 12345678910111213141516171819202122//将base64转换为blobbaseToBlob: function(data) &#123; var arr = data.split(&#x27;,&#x27;), mime = arr[0].match(/:(.*?);/)[1], bstr = atob(arr[1]), n = bstr.length, u8arr = new Uint8Array(n); while (n--) &#123; u8arr[n] = bstr.charCodeAt(n); &#125; return new Blob([u8arr], &#123; type: mime &#125;);&#125;,//将blob转换为fileblobToFile: function(blob, fileName)&#123; blob.lastModifiedDate = new Date(); blob.name = fileName; return blob;&#125;,//调用var blob = baseToBlob(base64Data);var file = blobToFile(blob, imgName);","categories":[{"name":"常用代码&开发中的问题","slug":"常用代码-开发中的问题","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/categories/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"}],"tags":[]},{"title":"常用代码&开发中的问题","slug":"常用代码&开发中的问题","date":"2022-06-26T04:37:55.646Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:18.000Z","comments":true,"path":"常用代码&开发中的问题/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81&%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Git","slug":"其他/Git","date":"2022-06-21T13:28:32.615Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"其他/Git/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Git/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"其他","slug":"其他","date":"2022-06-21T13:28:32.472Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"其他/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Unity","slug":"游戏开发/Unity","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:30.015Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"游戏开发/Unity/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/Unity/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"C基础","slug":"游戏开发/C#基础","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:30.012Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"游戏开发/C#基础/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/C#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/","excerpt":"","text":"C#概述简介C#（See Sharp），是一种新式编程语言，不仅面向对象还类型安全。开发人员利用 C# 能够生成在 .NET 中运行的多种安全可靠的应用程序。 C#是面向对象，面向组件的编程语言。C# 提供了语言构造来直接支持这些概念，让 C# 成为一种非常自然的语言，可用于创建和使用软件组件。 自诞生之日起，C# 就添加了支持新工作负载和新兴软件设计实践的功能。 C# 本质上是面向对象的语言。 你需要定义类型及其行为。","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Blender","slug":"游戏开发/Blender","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:30.011Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"游戏开发/Blender/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/Blender/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"语法","slug":"英语/语法","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:30.005Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"英语/语法/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"单词本","slug":"英语/单词本","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:30.002Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"英语/单词本/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E6%9C%AC/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"高等数学","slug":"数学/高等数学","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.998Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"数学/高等数学/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"离散数学","slug":"数学/离散数学","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.996Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"数学/离散数学/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/%E7%A6%BB%E6%95%A3%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Redis","slug":"数据库/Redis","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.991Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"数据库/Redis/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/Redis/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Oracle","slug":"数据库/Oracle","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.989Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"数据库/Oracle/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/Oracle/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"MySQL","slug":"数据库/MySQL","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.987Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"数据库/MySQL/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/MySQL/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Vue","slug":"前端/Vue","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.982Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"前端/Vue/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/Vue/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"JavaScript","slug":"前端/JavaScript","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.980Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"前端/JavaScript/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/JavaScript/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/categories/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/tags/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/"},{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/tags/JavaScript/"}]},{"title":"HTML和CSS","slug":"前端/HTML和CSS","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.978Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"前端/HTML和CSS/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/HTML%E5%92%8CCSS/","excerpt":"","text":"网站概述网站概述网站是指在因特网上根据一定的规则，使用 HTML 等制作的用于展示特定内容相关的网页集合。 网页是网站中的一“页”，通常是 HTML 格式的文件，它要通过浏览器来阅读。 网页是构成网站的基本元素，它通常由图片、链接、文字、声音、视频等元素组成。通常我们看到的网页，常见以 .htm 或 .html 后缀结尾的文件，因此将其俗称为 HTML 文件。 常用浏览器 IE 火狐 谷歌 Safari（苹果浏览器） Opera（欧朋） 浏览器内核浏览器内核主要负责读取网页内容，整理讯息，计算网页的显示方式并显示页面。 浏览器 内核 备注 IE Trident 国内大多数浏览器都使用这个 火狐 Gecko Safari Webkit 谷歌/欧朋 Blink Blink其实是Webkit的分支 Web标准Web标准是由W3C和其他标准化组织制定的一系列标准的集合。W3C（万维网联盟）是国际最著名的标准化组织。 统一的Web标准不仅可以让开发人员的代码更加规范，还可以： 让Web发展前景更加广阔 内容能被更多的设备访问 更容易被搜索引擎搜索 降低网站流量费用 使网站更加容易维护 提高页面的速度 Web标准主要由：结构，表现，行为三个方面构成： 结构：用于对网页元素进行整理和分类，HTML 表现：用于设置网页元素的样式，CSS 行为：对网页模型的定义以及交互的编写，JavaScript Web标准提出最佳体验方案：结构，样式，行为相互分离，即：HTML写在html文件中，css写在css文件中，JavaScript写在js文件中。 HTMLHTML概述HTML（Hyper Text Markup Language），指超文本标记语言，是一种用来表述网页的语言。 HTML不是编程语言，而是一种标记语言，即标记标签。 HTML文件通常以.html或.htm结尾。 HTML标签是由尖括号包围的关键字，例如：。 HTML标签通常是成对出现的，例如，，这样的标签也被称为双标签。第一为开始标签，第二个为结束标签，标签内可以嵌套其他标签。 还有一些特殊的标签会以单个形式出现，例如：，这样的标签被称为单标签。 标签之间的关系可以分为包含和并列关系。如： html标签包含h1和h2 h1和h2为并列关系 1234&lt;html&gt; &lt;h1&gt;&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/html&gt; HTML标签基本结构标签每个页面都会有一些基本的结构标签（骨架标签）。 标签名 定义 说明 html HTML标签 页面中最大的标签，也被称为根标签 head 文档的头部 设置网页头部信息 title 文档的标题 设置网页标题，是head中必须要设置的标签 body 文档的主体 文档的主题，页面的内容基本都写在这里面 HTML的基本结构 12345678910111213&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;&lt;head&gt; &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt; &lt;title&gt;基本结构标签&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt; &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; 文档类型声明标签，告诉浏览器这个页面采取html5版本来显示页面。 lang属性用来定义当前文档的语言，不管定义成什么语言，都是可以显示其他语言的。 &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt; 规定HTML文档使用哪种字符集。 标题标签 &lt;h1&gt;~&lt;h6&gt;123456&lt;h1&gt;我是h1&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;我是h2&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;我是h3&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4&gt;我是h4&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h5&gt;我是h5&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h6&gt;我是h6&lt;/h6&gt; 一个标题独占一行 文字会加粗，h1刀h6字号逐渐减小 段落标签 &lt;p&gt;1&lt;p&gt;我是段落标签&lt;/p&gt; 文本在段落标签中会根据浏览器的大小自动换行 段落和段落之间会有空隙 换行标签 &lt;br /&gt;11111111&lt;br /&gt;111111 换行标签是一个单标签 就是简单的开始下一行 文本格式化标签 含义 标签 加粗 &lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 或者&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt; 倾斜 &lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;或者&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt; 删除线 &lt;del&gt;&lt;del&gt; 或者&lt;s&gt;&lt;/s&gt; 下划线 &lt;ins&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; 或者&lt;u&gt;&lt;/u&gt; 盒子标签&lt;div&gt;和&lt;span&gt;div和span是没有语义的就是一个盒子，用来装内容。 div标签主要用来布局，一行只能放一个 span标签一行可以放多个 图像标签&lt;img&gt;1&lt;img src=&quot;图像URL&quot;&gt; 属性 属性 含义 src 图片路径 alt 替换文本，图片不能正常显示时文字 title 提示文本，鼠标移动到图片上时，显示的文字 width 图像宽度 height 图像高度 border 设置图像的边框 可以同时写多个属性，属性没有先后顺序 属性采用键值对的方式 链接标签&lt;a&gt;1&lt;a href=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 属性 属性 含义 取值 href 跳转的目标 链接，html页面，#（空链接）… target 用于指定链接页面的打开方式 _self（默认值），_blank新窗口打开 分类： 外部链接：例如：百度网址 内部链接，跳转到其他html页面 空链接：hred值为# 下载链接：当href的值为一个文件或者压缩包时，会下载这个文件 网页元素链接：给网页中的各种文本，图像，视频等都可以添加超链接 锚点链接：点击链接快速定位到页面中的某个位置，将href的值设置为#名字的形式，将目标位置的标签里添加id属性，名字就是这个id属性 注释1&lt;!--我是注释--&gt; 注释不会参与代码的执行，为了对代码进行解释说明，提高代码可读性。 特殊字符不需要记忆，需要使用时查阅便可以了 含义 字符代码 空格 &amp;nbsp; 小于号 &amp;lt; 大于号 &amp;gt; 和号 &amp;amp; 人民币 &amp;yen; 版权 &amp;copy; 注册商标 &amp;reg; 摄氏度 &amp;deg; 正负号 &amp;plusmn; 乘号 &amp;times; 除号 &amp;divide; 平方 &amp;sup2; 立方 &amp;sup3; HTML5CSS","categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/categories/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/tags/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF/"},{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/tags/HTML/"},{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/tags/CSS/"}]},{"title":"设计模式","slug":"计算机专业课/设计模式","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.971Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"计算机专业课/设计模式/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%AF%BE/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"计算机网络","slug":"计算机专业课/计算机网络","date":"2022-06-21T13:03:29.970Z","updated":"2022-06-26T04:37:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"计算机专业课/计算机网络/","link":"","permalink":"https://hyc-coderoad.github.io.git/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%AF%BE/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E